Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.07,0:22:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,小步 要保密哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.28,0:22:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我和老公很多年没做爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.55,0:22:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,原因是年纪大了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.29,0:22:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,女人的魅力也失去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.63,0:22:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,但是小步
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.09,0:23:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,把我当成女人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.56,0:23:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.25,0:23:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,一直以来被人渴求的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.32,0:23:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在才明白
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.15,0:23:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.89,0:24:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.23,0:24:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,老公 喝太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.03,0:24:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麽关系  明天休息
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.37,0:24:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.50,0:24:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,明天休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.71,0:24:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你要出门吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.51,0:24:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,和朋友约好了
