Dialogue: 0,1:53:59.42,1:54:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: 0,1:54:01.02,1:54:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,去了 去了
Dialogue: 0,1:54:29.98,1:54:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,舔吧
Dialogue: 0,1:54:59.54,1:55:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,还有时间呢
Dialogue: 0,1:55:00.88,1:55:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,和我接吻吧
Dialogue: 0,1:55:34.91,1:55:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,幸福的家庭时间
Dialogue: 0,1:55:38.78,1:55:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,以前我以为会一直持续下去
Dialogue: 0,1:55:44.05,1:55:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,但是现在我只想要和小步\N单独相处的时间
Dialogue: 0,1:55:54.13,1:55:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,1:55:57.00,1:55:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:55:58.20,1:55:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我给你的
Dialogue: 0,1:56:00.00,1:56:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好开心哦
Dialogue: 0,1:56:04.81,1:56:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,吹蜡烛吧
Dialogue: 0,1:56:07.08,1:56:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,1:56:13.28,1:56:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,1:56:14.88,1:56:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,好害羞哦
Dialogue: 0,1:56:20.69,1:56:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,要身体健康哦
Dialogue: 0,1:56:24.63,1:56:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好开心
Dialogue: 0,1:56:25.56,1:56:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,年纪不小了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:56:27.03,1:56:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,还很年轻呢
Dialogue: 0,1:56:31.17,1:56:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,1:56:32.70,1:56:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,吃吧
Dialogue: 0,1:56:34.57,1:56:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,1:56:44.85,1:56:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,1:56:45.98,1:56:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,1:56:51.39,1:56:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,已经这个年纪了
Dialogue: 0,1:56:53.39,1:56:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,要注意身体健康哦
Dialogue: 0,1:56:55.59,1:56:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系的 想喝就喝
Dialogue: 0,1:56:58.59,1:57:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,少喝点酒吧
Dialogue: 0,1:57:00.73,1:57:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那就没意思了
Dialogue: 0,1:57:02.60,1:57:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这样子会有高血压的
Dialogue: 0,1:57:07.14,1:57:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,和这个没关系
Dialogue: 0,1:57:08.67,1:57:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,有关系的
Dialogue: 0,1:57:11.61,1:57:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我最注意的
Dialogue: 0,1:57:14.61,1:57:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不要这么说
Dialogue: 0,1:57:17.68,1:57:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,下次是什麽时候
Dialogue: 0,1:57:20.48,1:57:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我只在乎这个
Dialogue: 0,1:57:26.29,1:57:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,
